<title>ạ̉ṭlb wjhk dh kfạyẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạ̉ṭlb wjhk yạ sydy .. ạ̉ʿbd ạsmk yạ sydy
 qlby yḥbk .. nfsy tḥbk .. ṭlbty mjdk yạ sydy
 ạ̉nt kl mạ fyã yạ sydy .. ạ̉nt kl mạ lyã yạ sydy
 ạ̉nt ḥạjty ạ̉nt qwty .. (ạ̉nt kfạyty yạ sydy)2

[V2]
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̉ṭlb wjhk dh kfạyẗ .. ạ̉nẓr wjhk dh sẖfạyạ)2
 (msẖ mstny yạ rby mnk .. ạ̹lạ syrk wyạyạ)2
 1- (tḥt ẓlk ntwạʿd .. nmsẖy mʿaⁿạ wlạ ntbạʿd)2
 (qlby mryḍ bḥbk rby .. mạ bysẖbʿ mnh kfạyẗ)2
 2- (kl mạ fyã bysẖtạq lyk .. ljlsẗ ʿnd qdmyk)2
 (ạ̉ḥky lk bsẖwqy wạnt .. tḥky bạlrwḥ jwạyạ)2
 3- (gẖny̱ wkrạmẗ ạ̉ʿṭytny .. qnyẗ fạkẖrẗ ạ̉gẖnytny)2
 (sẖbʿạn ạ̉nạ msẖ ṭạlb ạ̹lạ ạ̹nt .. dh ạnt tạjy whnạyạ)2
 4- (ḥb yswʿ wạḍḥ mʿrwf .. ḥbh mlạny wṭrd ạlkẖwf)2
 (ḥbk dwạʾ ḥqyqy mwṣwf .. bạlqy̱ fyh kl ḥmạyẗ)2</lyrics>
</song>